            <h2 class="title"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/coronavirus-live-updates/2020/04/17/837347535/nih-launches-effort-to-speed-up-development-of-covid-19-treatments"  data-metrics='{"action":"Click Story Title","category":"Story List"}' >NIH Launches Effort To Speed Up Development Of COVID-19 Treatments</a></h2>
            

            <div class="bucketwrap byline" id="res837352201" previewTitle="bylines">
